Cam::

She made her way to the outside of the base.  She followed her nose 
futher still from the base.  She sniffed the ground, her nose firmly 
following the trail of the strange scent.  She was just to determind 
to not stop but to find out why the strange scent was there and whom 
it came from.  She was far outside the base and a few miles from the 
base by nightfall.


Sleep was to finally over take her.  She curled up in fox mode under 
a tree and slept soundly.
